===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# An implement for eating or serving; a [[scoop]]ed [[utensil]] whose long handle is straight, in contrast to a [[ladle]].
# An implement for stirring food while being prepared; a [[wooden spoon]].
# {{cattag|sports|archaic}} A wooden-headed [[golf club]] with moderate loft, similar to the modern [[three wood]].
# {{cattag|fishing}} A type of metal [[lure]] resembling the [[concave]] head of a [[table spoon]].

